WEBVTT

00:01:57.375 --> 00:02:00.393
(Laughter)

00:02:00.417 --> 00:02:04.018
We have to live simply,
so that others can simply live.

00:02:04.042 --> 00:02:06.351
And when we think
of the kind of inheritance

00:02:06.375 --> 00:02:09.726
that we want to leave to our children
or our grandchildren,

00:02:09.750 --> 00:02:12.809
think of leaving them a legacy of justice.

00:02:12.833 --> 00:02:15.476
This is a legacy
that they can not only imitate,

00:02:15.500 --> 00:02:18.643
but they can be proud of
for the rest of their lives.

00:02:18.667 --> 00:02:22.643
If we leave them a lot of material goods,
all they're going to do is fight,

00:02:22.667 --> 00:02:24.476
and they're going to hate each other.

00:02:24.500 --> 00:02:27.559
Just remember that,
when we think about what we're doing.

00:02:27.583 --> 00:02:32.184
